Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:25.21,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\fn汉仪颜楷W\b0\bord3\blur6\shad0\fs160\fsp50\1cE7E84D\3cF5FEF7\pos(1038,800)}约会
